        <h3><a name="Get_Widget_Code"></a>Get Widget Code</h3>
        <p>To get started, just use the configurator to get code to add to your site.</p>
        <h4>Settings:</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><p><code>API Key</code> - the Key for Edmunds API registered on <a href="http://developer.edmunds.com" target="_blank">Edmunds Developer Portal</a>.</p></li>
            <li><p><code>Default Zip Code</code> - the zip code to display by default in ZIP field.</p></li>
            <li><p><code>VIN code</code> - car's vin code </p></li>
            <li><p><code>Width</code> - sets the width of the Widget.</p></li>
            <li><p><code>Get Code</code> - instructions to embed Edmunds At A Glance Widget on your page.</p></li>
        </ul>

        <hr class="bs-docs-separator">

        <h3><a name="How_to_Embed_Widget"></a>How to Embed Widget</h3>
        <p>To embed Edmunds Price Promise Widget on your page just follow the instructions from <code>Get Code</code> popup.</p>
        <h4>Example scenario:</h4>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <p>Insert the empty div to your page:</p>
                <pre>&lt;div id="ppb-&lt;vin will add here automatically&gt;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</pre>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Add the following JavaScript snippet to your page:</p>
                <pre>
&lt;script type="text/javascript" src="http://widgets.edmunds.com/loader-ppb.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;
(function(){
var widget = EDM.createWidget({
    "type": "ppb",
    "renderTo": "ppb-&lt;vin will add here automatically&gt;",
    "style": {
        "width": "250",
        "height": "630"
    },
    "scripts": [
        "/libs/requirejs/require.js\" data-main=\"http://widgets.edmunds.com/ppb/js/main.js"
    ],
    "options": {
        "apiKey": &lt;api key&gt;
        "vin": &lt;car's vin&gt;,
        "zipCode": "90404"
    }
});
}());
&lt;/script&gt;
                </pre>
            </li>
        </ol>

